Package: ux570-importer
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-yaml
Recommends: python3-pyqt6
Description: Import recordings from Sony ICD-UX570 Digital Voice Recorder
 A utility to import recordings from a Sony ICD-UX570 Digital Voice Recorder,
 organizing them by month and day automatically. Supports both command-line
 and graphical user interface modes.
 .
 Features:
  - Automatic date-based organization of recordings
  - Move or copy modes
  - SHA256 checksum generation
  - GUI interface (with PyQt6)
